[SPEAKER_05]: Yes, I think I have quite a lot of them tonight, actually.

147
00:10:03,704 --> 00:10:13,413
[SPEAKER_05]: So for Electrify Medford, a press release about the grant went out towards the end of February.

148
00:10:15,455 --> 00:10:20,559
[SPEAKER_05]: We're still waiting to get the contract signed with Mass EEC.

149
00:10:21,020 --> 00:10:26,464
[SPEAKER_05]: And we still need to get more information up on the website, make flyers, and prepare those materials and stuff.

150
00:10:26,985 --> 00:10:29,607
[SPEAKER_05]: But that's where we are right now.

151
00:10:30,127 --> 00:10:35,632
[SPEAKER_05]: So far, 21 people have signed up to be energy coaches, which I think is wonderful.

152
00:10:36,673 --> 00:10:41,417
[SPEAKER_05]: We're interviewing each one of them to better match them up with interested residents.

153
00:10:42,978 --> 00:10:48,668
[SPEAKER_05]: And then we'll let folks know if they're eligible for stipends and schedule our first training session in about two weeks.

154
00:10:51,812 --> 00:11:04,017
[SPEAKER_05]: I'm still going through the internal process to hire the heat pump consultant who's going to be doing training and going to be working with residents who are interested in switching to heat pumps.

155
00:11:04,597 --> 00:11:13,840
[SPEAKER_05]: But some good news, MassAve actually now offers heat pump consultations for free with the consultant that we were looking to hire.

156
00:11:15,681 --> 00:11:16,943
[SPEAKER_05]: That's going to save us some money.

157
00:11:16,963 --> 00:11:17,724
[SPEAKER_05]: That's great.

158
00:11:18,785 --> 00:11:26,773
[SPEAKER_05]: They're not doing right now the quote comparison tool and the energy coach training, which were the other aspects of the contract with a consultant.

159
00:11:26,813 --> 00:11:28,836
[SPEAKER_05]: So we'll still need to be paying for that right now.

160
00:11:29,877 --> 00:11:34,742
[SPEAKER_05]: But MassSave is actually looking into offering both of those as well.

161
00:11:34,802 --> 00:11:37,185
[SPEAKER_05]: They're just not quite on the same timeline that we are.

162
00:11:40,980 --> 00:11:45,662
[SPEAKER_05]: Um, we're still working on the internal process for the resident incentives.

163
00:11:46,782 --> 00:11:52,185
[SPEAKER_05]: Um, so more to come for that probably, um, and towards the end of March.

164
00:11:53,805 --> 00:12:00,688
[SPEAKER_05]: Um, and we're looking probably at a soft launch towards the end of March and then a real public kickoff in April.

165
00:12:06,290 --> 00:12:08,371
[SPEAKER_05]: Um, any questions about Electrify Medford?

166
00:12:13,588 --> 00:12:17,692
[SPEAKER_02]: I want to say congratulations on the grant.

167
00:12:17,792 --> 00:12:18,312
[SPEAKER_02]: It's great.

168
00:12:19,413 --> 00:12:20,474
[SPEAKER_02]: It's really exciting.

169
00:12:21,074 --> 00:12:33,024
[SPEAKER_02]: It's a challenge to bring that kind of clean energy to low and middle income.

170
00:12:34,015 --> 00:12:38,656
[SPEAKER_02]: households, particularly in the single family situation.

171
00:12:39,676 --> 00:12:46,417
[SPEAKER_02]: I'm really proud of Medford for taking that on and look forward to seeing what happens.

172
00:12:48,638 --> 00:12:57,740
[SPEAKER_05]: I think this coach model is going to be really helpful in reaching different populations than maybe we would have with more general outreach.

173
00:12:59,560 --> 00:12:59,700
[SPEAKER_05]: Yeah.

174
00:13:04,023 --> 00:13:06,184
[SPEAKER_05]: Moving on to curbside composting.

175
00:13:06,784 --> 00:13:11,005
[SPEAKER_05]: The press release for this went out at the end of January.

176
00:13:13,026 --> 00:13:21,628
[SPEAKER_05]: People can sign up for it at medfordcomposts.com and I'll drop this in the chat too in case people hear.

177
00:13:23,648 --> 00:13:31,552
[SPEAKER_05]: are still looking to sign up so yes, some people can sign up now to be put on a wait list for the free composting service July 1.

178
00:13:33,333 --> 00:13:40,377
[SPEAKER_05]: Or you can sign up now to pay you know them a monthly fee just to start immediately and then it'll automatically switch over on July 1.

179
00:13:47,010 --> 00:13:55,999
