00:36:37,725 --> 00:36:40,327
[SPEAKER_09]: So, I don't have a date yet, they'll let us know.

381
00:36:42,749 --> 00:36:56,500
[SPEAKER_09]: And that will go to the committee of the whole, they're hoping sometime, oh, this is March already, but time is moving along, and have the city council will have their

