383
00:37:04,189 --> 00:37:13,219
[SPEAKER_09]: Well, it's not the law department, they're a consulting legal group, KP Law Review for their suggestions too.

384
00:37:13,239 --> 00:37:19,385
[SPEAKER_09]: Let's see, the suggestions were made in the private ordinance.

